![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7fa532d0-ee29-4692-8eec-4ba5c1808e3b/PhotoGrid_1_20240403015427.jpg)

Jared Krichevsky, the Lead Creature Designer on Godzilla X Kong: the New Empire, revealed that Godzilla's Powered Up Pink Form is based off of Goku's Kaioken from the Dragon Ball series.

This was revealed during an "Ask Me Almost Anything" session on his Twitter/X account (@MonsterMash042)

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6fed8b0e-f110-4e89-acca-60292abe78a7/Screenshot_20240403_020928.jpg)